    Gronda is a text editor inspired by the AEGIS Display Manager editor 
    found on Apollo/Domain workstations. 

    System Requirements:

    Unix/Linux or Mac OS X
    FLTK 1.3 for the graphical interface
    ncurses for the terminal interface (currently not working)
